{"lemma":"حُكْمُ","slug":"حُكْمُ","root":"ح.ك.م","root_slug":"ح-ك-م","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-ك-م","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"حُكْم","root":"حكم","pos":"N","occurrence_count":30},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":8,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":32},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n8714","n8715"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D9%8F%D9%83%D9%92%D9%85%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to exercise authority, command, bid, to rule, to reign, to decree"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to hit upon, to obtain"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to happen, to arrive, to befall"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to deliver a sentence, to judge between"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to bridle; to put the bit to a bridle"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to restrain, to withhold, to rein"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to keep, to preserve, to protect"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be wise"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to establish solidly"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to appoint as a judge or governor"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to bid to give full judgment"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to give full powers"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to process farther, to produce, to develop, to metabolize"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of حَكَمَ (ḥakama, “to command, to judge, to sentence”) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"sentence, judgment"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"jurisdiction"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"power, authority"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"magistrate"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"government"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"decree, command, precept"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"rule of life"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"prediction from the stars"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"fate, predestination"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"knowledge, wisdom"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"reason, cause, ground"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"category"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"regard"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of حَكَمَ (ḥakama, “to bridle”) (form I), bridling","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"judge, arbitrator"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"commander"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"referee"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of حِكْمَة (ḥikma)","tags":["form-of","plural"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ħa.ka.ma/","/ħa.ku.ma/","/ħak.ka.ma/","/ħukm/","/ħakm/","/ħa.kam/","/ħi.kam/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n8714","headword_ar":"حُكْمٌ","root":"Hkm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[inf. n. of 1, q. v.,] originally signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Prevention,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"restraint."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) ―         -b2-  And hence, (Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Judgment,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"judicial decision:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"judgment respecting a thing, that it is such a thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is not such a thing, whether it be necessarily connected with another thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) [whence,] in logic, [what our logicians term"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"judgment;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"judging a thing to stand to another"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thing"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the relation of an attribute to its subject, affirmatively"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"negatively;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perception of relation"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"non-relation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Kull:) or it properly signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"judgment with equity"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"justice:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Az, TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HukuwmapN","text_ar":"حُكُومَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same; (K, TA;) originally, accord. to As, the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"restraint"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a man from"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wrongdoing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) [each, though an inf. n., being used as a simple subst., has its pl.:] the pl. of the former is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHokaAmN","text_ar":"اَحْكَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) [properly a pl. of pauc., but] its only pl. form: and the pl. of the latter is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HukuwmaAtN","text_ar":"حُكُومَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wa yafoSilu","text_ar":"وَ يَفْصِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa yatawal~aY AlHukuwmaAti","text_ar":"هُوَ يَتَوَلَّى الحُكُومَاتِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlxuSuwmaAti","text_ar":"الخُصُومَاتِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He presides over the affairs of judgment, and decides litigations"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And it is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~a mina Al$~iEori laHukomFA","text_ar":"اـِنَّ مِنَ الشِّعْرِ لَحُكْمًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily, of poetry, there is"},{"kind":"text","text":"that which is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"true judgment:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so says Er-Rághib: or, as others say,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"profitable discourse, such as restrains from, and forbids, ignorant and silly behaviour;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e., [what contains] exhortations and proverbs profitable to men: or, the right reading is, as some relate it, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laHikomapF","text_ar":"لَحِكْمَةً","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wisdom,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HikamFA","text_ar":"حِكَمًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hikomap","text_ar":"حِكْمَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (So in a copy of the “ Jámi' es-Sagheer ” of Es-Suyootee.) ―         -b3-  [The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exercise of judicial authority; jurisdiction; rule; dominion;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"government."},{"kind":"text","text":"See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HukuwmapN","text_ar":"حُكُومَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An ordinance; a statute; a prescript; an edict; a decree;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a particular law;"},{"kind":"text","text":"like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaDaA='N","text_ar":"قَضَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". Hence the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hukoma AlEaAdapi","text_ar":"حُكْمَ العَادَةِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"According to custom"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"usage;"},{"kind":"text","text":"properly,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"according to the ordinance of custom"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"usage."},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b5-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A rule"},{"kind":"text","text":"in grammar &c.; as when one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hukomu AlfaAEili Alr~afoEu","text_ar":"حُكْمُ الفَاعِلِ الرَّفْعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ano yurofaEa","text_ar":"اَنْ يُرْفَعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The rule applying to the case of the agent is that it be put in the nom. case;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hukomuhu Hukomu ka*aA","text_ar":"حُكْمُهُ حُكْمُ كَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaHukomi","text_ar":"كَحُكْمِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"k*A","text_ar":"كذا"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The rule applying to it is"},{"kind":"text","text":"the same as"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the rule applying to such a thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like the rule applying to such a thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b6-  It may often be rendered"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Predicament:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(thus the last of the foregoing exs. may be rendered"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Its predicament is"},{"kind":"text","text":"the same as"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the predicament of such a thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like the predicament of such a thing:"},{"kind":"text","text":") and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HukomFA","text_ar":"حُكْمًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY AlHukomi","text_ar":"فِى الحُكْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"predicamentally,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in respect of predicament;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"virtually;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as distinguished from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lafoZFA","text_ar":"لَفْظًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(literally), and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaqiyqapF","text_ar":"حَقِيقَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":"(really), and the like.] ―         -b7-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Knowledge of the law in matters of religion."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b8-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HikomapN","text_ar":"حِكْمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places. It is a more general term than"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HikomapN","text_ar":"حِكْمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; for all"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hikomap","text_ar":"حِكْمَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hukom","text_ar":"حُكْم"},{"kind":"text","text":", but the reverse is not the case. (Er-Rághib, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","S","K","TA","Kull","Az"]},{"entry_id":"n8715","headword_ar":"حَكَمٌ","root":"Hkm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAkimN","text_ar":"حَاكِمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muHak~imN","text_ar":"مُحَكِّمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHakamu","text_ar":"الحَكَمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The Judge"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is one of the names of God. (TA.) ―         -b2-  A man"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"advanced in age"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the utmost degree."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HakamapN","text_ar":"حَكَمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["K","TA"]}]}}